## Components

### Driver Program
- Runs the main() function
- Creates SparkSession
- Coordinates executors

### Cluster Manager
- Allocates resources
- Manages worker nodes
- Supports Standalone, YARN, Kubernetes

### Executor
- Runs tasks on worker nodes
- Stores data in memory/disk
- Reports metrics to driver

### Task
- Unit of work on a partition
- One task per partition per stage
- Executed by executor threads
